text.tspan: It appears at dusk, disappears at dawn,
never twice at the same location.
The dream is ever-changing after all.

tspan.tspan: Your Corrupted cards in and out of play have Kharmic.
You cannot take more Kharmic actions each turn than the

text.tspan: number of your Ephemeral Shrines in play.
